info.description:
Example Code:

>>> # instagram video downloader
>>> import inface-dl
>>> ses = inface-dl.Session()
>>> ses.ig(url='url here', output='output.mp4')


>>> # facebook video downloader
>>> import inface-dl
>>> ses = inface-dl.Session()
>>> ses.fb(url='url here', output='output.mp4')
